Notepad App
A simple, lightweight HTML5-based notepad app that lets you type, save, and manage notes directly in your browser. Notes are stored locally using localStorage, so they persist even after refreshing the page.

Features:
Type and edit notes in a user-friendly text area.
Save notes locally in the browser with one click.
Automatically loads saved notes on page reload.
Clear notes easily with a confirmation prompt.
How to Use:
Clone or download the repository.
Open the notepad.html file in any web browser.
Start typing, save your notes, and enjoy!
Future Enhancements (Optional):
Export and import notes as text files.
Add dark mode for better usability.
